        public PublisherConfiguration.Builder streamLifeCycle(int lifecycle)
        Deprecated. 
        CDN push stream life cycle

        You can choose:

        • Bind to channel (STREAM_LIFE_CYCLE_BIND2CHANNEL) or
        • Bind to room owner (STREAM_LIFE_CYCLE_BIND2OWNER).
